      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46). This S54 powerplant is a masterpiece of atmospheric induction, featuring high-pressure Double-VANOS and individual throttle bodies that deliver a razor-sharp throttle response up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional rotational torque distribution. Meticulously serviced with recent rod bearing replacement and shim-regulated valve adjustments, this chassis remains as rigid and communicative as the day it left Regensburg. No stone chips, no bolster wear, and a flawless underbody.",
      "price": 49200.0,
